snippet.title: Gordian Rooms: A curious heritage Trailer
snippet.description:
Buy the game here:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1285080/Gordian_Rooms_A_curious_heritage/

Gordian Rooms: A curious heritage is a Victorian escape game, where you solve various puzzles in your late uncle’s mansion in the hope of obtaining his legacy.
